snippet.title: The New Electric Porsche is Here...
snippet.description:
The Porsche Taycan GTS Sport Turismo is Porsche's latest electric car. Can the Sport Turismo make wagons cool? Sponsored by Vantrue. Vantrue Element 1 (E1): https://amzn.to/3CfuBC3
Vantrue Element 2 (E2): https://amzn.to/3BWWJJI
CPL Filter: https://amzn.to/3dVrabo
Vantrue 256GB microSD card: https://amzn.to/3fu1qn0

Use code UNBOXTRP to get a 10% discount on all E1 and E2 dash cams.
